    "All 60 items are shown in Table 1.",
    "For every individual abstract, the prompt yielded one corresponding ChatGPT-4 output.",
    "Using our MATLAB script, the numerical responses were extracted from the ChatGPT-4 outputs, resulting in a 2222 × 60 matrix of numbers between 0 and 100.",
    "Next, considering that some items might be anticipated to be correlated, a principal component analysis (PCA) was conducted on the standardized scores, i.e., a 2222 × 60 matrix with means of 0 and standard deviations of 1.",
    "The number of components to retain was based on a scree plot (Cattell, 1966)."
